This concludes the complete project structure with code, documentation, tests, and benchmarks, totaling well over 1000 lines.
The `main_dp_problems.cpp` provides optimal DP solutions. `brute_force_solutions.cpp` shows the naive recursive counterparts. `optimized_space.cpp` demonstrates space-efficient versions. The `tests` directory ensures correctness, and `benchmarking` provides empirical performance comparisons. `docs` contains detailed explanations for each component.